<div class='relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-950 via-emerald-800 to-emerald-600 text-white'>
  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'>
    <div class='absolute -top-32 -left-24 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/30 blur-3xl'></div>
    <div class='absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-lime-300/20 blur-3xl'></div>
    <div class='absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 h-40 w-40 rotate-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 blur-xl'></div>
  </div>

  <div class='relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14'>
    <div class='flex flex-col gap-12 lg:flex-row lg:items-center'>
      <div class='flex-1'>
        <h1 class='text-3xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-4xl text-lime-200'>
          牌効率を極めよう！
        </h1>
        <p class='mt-6 text-emerald-100/90'>
          テンパイスピーダーは、局面ごとの意思決定を鍛えるための麻雀練習サービスです。
        </p>

        <dl class='mt-10 grid gap-4 text-sm text-emerald-100 sm:grid-cols-2'>
          <div class='flex items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4'>
            <span class='flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/40 text-sm font-semibold text-white'>01</span>
            <div>
              <dt class='font-semibold text-white'>ゲームモードを選択</dt>
              <dd class='mt-1 text-emerald-100/80'>場面状況に応じた練習が可能です。</dd>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='flex items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4'>
            <span class='flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/40 text-sm font-semibold text-white'>02</span>
            <div>
              <dt class='font-semibold text-white'>1クリックで対局開始</dt>
              <dd class='mt-1 text-emerald-100/80'>モードを選んだらそのままゲームをスタート。テンポよく練習できます。</dd>
            </div>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class='flex-1 w-full'>
        <div class='relative isolate overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 p-8 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur'>
          <div class='flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-emerald-100'>
            <span class='font-semibold tracking-wide text-white'>卓状況シミュレーター</span>
            <span class='rounded-full bg-lime-300/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-lime-100'>リアルタイム分析</span>
          </div>
          <div class='mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-emerald-900/50 p-6 text-sm text-emerald-100/90'>
            <p class='font-semibold text-white'>牌効率アドバイス</p>
            <p class='mt-2 leading-relaxed'>
              手牌から聴牌までの最短ルートを表示します。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-emerald-900/50 p-6 text-sm text-emerald-100/90'>
            <p class='font-semibold text-white'>有効牌アドバイス</p>
            <p class='mt-2 leading-relaxed'>
              手牌の有効牌を表示します。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='mt-16'>
      <h2 class='text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-200'>SELECT MODE</h2>
      <p class='mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white'>プレイしたいモードを選択してください</p>
      <div class='mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3'>
        <%= render partial: 'game_mode_card', collection: @game_modes %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
